name: American Ape: The Digital Comic Collection

metadata.description:
American Ape: Bored Ape Seeks Yacht Club #1.  This digital collectible comic cover grants the holder access to read a pdf of the full digital comic book for BASYC #1, including an extra 44 pages of lore and art.

Follow along with American Ape, inspired by BAYC #5636 as he travels through the metaverse in search of the legendary Bored Ape Yacht Club.

Now that he's officially a stranger in a strange land, will a case of mistaken identity lead American Ape to his demise at the hands of the Ape Mafia, Cheetah Gang, Gutter Gangs, or Mutant Cartel?
metadata.name: Bored Ape Seeks Yacht Club Issue #1
